lead_paragraph: The Canadian Formula One Grand Prix will go ahead next June after organizers reached an agreement in principal with the sport's commercial rights holders, Montreal mayor Denis Coderre said on Twitter.

headline.print_headline: Canadian GP to Go Ahead, Says Montreal Mayor
